5 steps to run the program:

1. Open broker.py
2. Open subscriber.py
3. Open publisher.py
4. In subscriber.py send " subscribe <broker_ip> <topic_name> "
5. In publisher.py send " publish <broker_ip> <topic_name> <data_to_publish> "

Addition: You can add more window of subscriber and publisher 

ps1. subscriber will be terminated if there is no response within 60 seconds.
ps2. publisher will be terminated if it not send data to broker within 60 seconds.

